OL,3,CHeartbroken mum's call for better
OL,4,Ccancer services after son's death
OL,6,FA mother whose teenage son died from a
OL,7,Frare form of blood cancer has joined
OL,8,Fcalls for better regional services and
OL,9,Ffacilities to help improve survival
OL,10,Frates.
OL,12,FIt follows the publication of a UK-
OL,13,Fwide blood cancer action plan,
OL,14,Flaunched today by Alliance MP Sorcha
OL,15,FEastwood.
OL,17,FOzzie was just 17 when he died in
OL,18,FSeptember 2020 after a two-year battle
OL,19,Fwith acute myeloid leukaemia - a rare
OL,20,Ftype of blood cancer.
