OL,4,Ccancer services after son's death
OL,6,F"He was such a character ... he loved
OL,7,Fhis guitar, he loved family life, he
OL,8,Floved rugby, he was just a good wee
OL,9,Flad growing up," his mum Miranda
OL,10,FRogers said.
OL,12,FAccording to Blood Cancer UK, blood
OL,13,Fcancer is the UK's third biggest
OL,14,Fcancer killer.
