OL,3,CHeartbroken mum's call for better
OL,4,Ccancer services after son's death
OL,6,FThe situation in Northern Ireland is
OL,7,Fof particular concern, due to a lack
OL,8,Fof facilities and services available
OL,9,Felsewhere in the UK - something Ozzie
OL,10,Fand his family experienced when he
OL,11,Ftransitioned from child to adult
OL,12,Fservices at the age of 16.
OL,14,F"Ozzie sent a message to the teenage
OL,15,Fcancer trust, to say the difference
OL,16,Fbetween children's - which was so
OL,17,Flovely, and adult was like being in
OL,18,Fprison," Miranda explained.
