OL,3,CHeartbroken mum's call for better
OL,4,Ccancer services after son's death
OL,6,FThe campaign for better services is a
OL,7,Fpersonal one for Sorcha Eastwood,
OL,8,Fwhose husband is battling a rare form
OL,9,Fof blood cancer.
OL,11,FFollowing today's report she has
OL,12,Fcalled for Northern Ireland to have
OL,13,Fits own regional blood cancer and
OL,14,Fhaematology centre so that patients do
OL,15,Fnot have to travel so far from home.
OL,17,F"Coming off the back of this report,
OL,18,Fthere is so much more that needs to be
OL,19,Fdone in terms of facilities, in terms
OL,20,Fof workforce - not just in Northern
OL,21,FIreland but across the UK," she said.
